modName: Craft Small Pipes, Large Pipes and Conduit
modShortDescription: More Crafting and Decorating Items. This mod allows you to craft Conduit and Pipes of different shapes and sizes so you can look as good as you survive!
modDescription:
More Crafting and Decorating Items. Your Base does not have to be bland! This mod allows you to craft Conduit and Pipes of different shapes and sizes so you can look as good as you survive!

Server side friendly, so just drop in and go.

**[Download](https://docs.google.com/uc?export=download&id=16-apo7n3xddn7tAA9GZ8pwzbOzk9EwpX)**

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/22347-craft-small-pipes-large-pipes-and-conduit/).
